   <meta name="description" content="Intuit Spaces facilitates sharing of office space between small business owners.
   We help established small businesses recoup office expenses by renting out their excess office space to start-ups.
   We help start-ups and home-based small businesses get a professional looking office for less. They can use it to
     meet clients, work without distractions at home and learn from the established business owners.">

   <meta name="keywords" content="Intuit spaces, office, office share, co-working, rent office, exchange office,
   extra office, excess office, share office, meet established business, small business network, rental office"/>

